text: Amin ud Din Khan (born 1 December 1960) is a Pakistani jurist who has been Justice of Supreme Court of Pakistan since 22 October 2019. He served on the Lahore High Court from 12 May 2011 to 22 October 2019. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Judges of the Lahore High Court Category:Pakistani judges Category:Justices of the Supreme Court of Pakistan
title: Aminuddin Khan
